replies.body:
@RiotSparkle So we are supposed to report nasty club tags under "inappropriate names" and just add a note? I've been meaning to ask for a while now as it's not really made super clear in the client. ^.^

Also, since I might have your attention, I wanted to confirm something else that I've seen circulating. Is it true that we only get that "we busted someone you reported" pop-up when the automated system applies a punishment? We don't get it if an actual Rioter had to do a review?

Sorry for the question spam. ^.^;
